resource.string: Query or modify the value of GID1/GID2.

Usage:
%s $ gid [gid1=xxxxxx] [gid2=xxxxxx]
Example: - gid Original GID1: FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF Original GID2: FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF - gid1 gid1=12 Original GID1: FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF Updated GID1: 12 FF FF FF FF FF FF FF Original GID2: FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF
